casebody.data:
ARIZONA, petitioner,
v.
Guy James GOODMAN. No. 18-391. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 14, 2019.

Motion of Arizona Voice for Crime Victims, Inc., et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of Michael C. Dorf, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Arizona denied.
